Congress approves transposition of Mifid, which came into force on November 1
Alongside its parliamentary formality, which ended today with the vote of the Congress of amendments incorporated into the bill in the Senate, the Government submitted to a public hearing the regulation that will develop the new law, with the objective of its entry into force before the end of the year.
The representatives of the various groups agreed to highlight the efforts of Members of Parliament and Senators to negotiate and agree to the best possible regulation to ensure investor protection and to regulate in detail the activities of the agencies so that markets function effectively.
The Mifid, which amends the Securities Market Law, involves the modernization of the financial markets, at a time when it strengthens the protection of the investor, improves the powers of the leaders of the National Securities Market Commission (CNMV) and promotes cooperation between the various leaders of the European Union.
The new regulation will allow financial consulting services to be provided to both specialised societal purposes and to natural or legal persons and creates a new type of financial services (ESIS), financial consulting firms (FCAs), which merge with securities firms, securities agencies and portfolio managers.
In addition, it is increasing the number of systems for the execution of transactions in financial instruments, so that it is possible to add to the regulated secondary markets multilateral trading systems and order internationalization systems, which compete with current stock exchange managers.
The Act also requires investment firms to disclose to the market information on key aspects of their business profile, risk exposure and forms of risk management and requires them to keep a record of all transactions they perform, to facilitate control by the CNMV.
Through the Congressional Economic Commission, several amendments have been added, one of which highlights that securitized debt will be considered a "complex" financial instrument given its high risk to the investor, which has been demonstrated with what happened with the debt of American high-risk mortgages (subprime).
In addition, they took advantage of the transposition of the management took the opportunity to legally delineate the functions that graduates in Economics can have 30 years after that in 1977, was approved, the royal decree that delineates the professional functions reserved for economists.
For its part, the Senate has incorporated the creation of new figures in the financial sector, such as the Ombudsman, who will work on behalf of a company, who will not require the authorization of the CNMV and who will be able to lend its services of marketing products and attracting new customers to different investment firms at the same time.
